<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="abc.css"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8" /><h1>7 Ways to Get PR Before You Can Afford to Hire a PR Manager</h1>
				
					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="7 Ways to Get PR Before You Can Afford to Hire a PR Manager" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20160323133724-pr-firm-agency-public-speaking-speech-journalist-interview-woman-reporter-press-voice-communication.jpeg" rel="share" />

					
							
								
				
				
